    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i'm just looking for general info then. like, if someone were taking both, is it medically common for them to react badly? i'm just trying to understand if it's actually a risk or if it's just one of those standard warnings they put on everything. if it's not a huge deal, i'll just take it tonight so i can sleep.",
